Title: Unfinished Business
Plot: Adama stages a boxing tournament on the Galactica to help the crew relax. The competitive atmosphere sets off a brutal match between Kara and Lee. Flashbacks from New Caprica reveal the origin and nature of their dispute.
ParentalRatingReason: M Violence,sexual references and offensive language
GuestStars: Luciana Carro, Nicki Clyne, Donnelly Rhodes, Tahmoh Penikett, Alessandro Juliani, Kandyse McClure, Kate Vernon, Christian Tessier
